text: Homonoea samarana is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Heller in 1924. It is known from the Philippines.BioLib.cz - Homonoea samarana. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Homonoeini Category:Beetles described in 1924
title: Homonoea samarana
